title: Killing of Alex Pretti by immigration agents fuels anger in traumatized Minneapolis
subhed: Two weeks after the death of Renee Good, Alex Pretti, a 37-year-old nurse, was killed during a confrontation between Border Patrol officers and residents in Minneapolis. Democrats are now threatening to block funding for the Department of Homeland Security, even if it means triggering another government shutdown.
byline: By Nicolas Chapuis (New York (United States) correspondent)

Germany moves closer to Italy as disagreements strain ties with France
subhed: Chancellor Friedrich Merz, accompanied by part of his government, met with Italian prime minister Giorgia Meloni in Italy on Friday. The leaders of the two countries, both with a longstanding Atlanticist tradition, advocated for new free trade agreements.

title: Venezuela and the US: A century of turbulent oil relations
subhed: At the heart of an energy partnership and later an ideological clash, oil turned Venezuela into a strategic ally for Washington, before turning it into a target of Donald Trump's ambitions.

title: Falling birth rate in France: 'We may be witnessing a period of very rapid and highly gendered social change'
subhed: The decline in the number of births should be seen in connection with the 'gender divergence' between increasingly progressive young women and increasingly conservative young men, observes economist Pauline Grosjean in her column.

title: Inside the workshop where dress forms are made
subhed: For 160 years, the French company Stockman has been handcrafting dress forms used by fashion designers, costume makers and aspiring stylists to refine their creations. This centuries-old expertise allows Stockman to meet custom requests from around the world.

Generative AI, psychiatry and the risks of self-service therapy
subhed: Millions of people use chatbots like ChatGPT to share their distress, and the scientific community has warned about the risks vulnerable people face. Generative AI has shaken up psychiatric consultations, fueled tech giants' ambitions and emerged as a credible tool for analyzing pathologies.

title: The RN's unspoken attraction to MAGA – and gradual ideological alignment
subhed: Like other European nationalists, Marine Le Pen has been put in a tough spot by Donald Trump's imperialist offensive. But the MAGA ideological campaign in Europe, of which France is a key target, has won over her Rassemblement National party over the past year.

title: 'We were walking in blood': Iran's doctors recount crackdown on protesters
subhed: From crowded emergency rooms to apocalyptic scenes in Iranian cities, healthcare workers told Le Monde about the violence that descended on protesters calling for the end of the Iranian regime from January 8.
